data.description:
Great rental property in desirable Belmont area! Total house square footage is 1,066sq ft. (including the basement). Freshly painted with newer windows. Good sized bedrooms with a full bath between and includes a walk in stand up shower in the basement. Wood floors. Living room with lots of windows, and a built-in on the side of the fireplace (dummy). Large eat-in kitchen, with 2 pantries and a built in corner shelf. Extended length one car detached garage. Private fenced back yard with a paver patio and walkway. Quaint with the built-ins and curved arch into the hallway. 

Total due at signing of lease ($2,200) includes:
-First month's rent: $1,100
-Security Deposit: $1,100

Qualifications:
-Minimum Income requirement is 3x rent ($3,300/month) 
-No Prior Evictions

*Please complete application to be considered. Message or call for any additional questions.

Tenant is responsible for all utilities (water, electricity, gas...etc). Small dogs less than 20lbs allowed with a pet fee of $25 / month.
